item.title: 100 errors anyone know?
item.dc:creator: @zoltanman zoltanman
item.description:
@zoltanman wrote:

You didn’t close a statement.

Ex:

Wrong

void methodOne() {
     if(missedBracket) {
        youMissedBracket++
}

Correct

void methodOne() {
     if(missedBracket) {
        youMissedBracket++
     }
}

You have to go back and make sure you closed every statement.
